---
const audience = [
  'People tired of conflicting dietary advice and one-size-fits-all protocols',
  'Anyone who wants data they can read and act on from home',
  'Those working through fatigue, brain fog, or gut issues',
];
---

<section class="section genes">
  <div class="container genes__grid">
    <div class="genes__copy">
      <p class="eyebrow" data-reveal>Your genes guide us, they don't define you</p>
      <h2 class="genes__title" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 0.06s">
        DNA as a navigation tool, not a crystal ball.
      </h2>
      <p class="prose" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 0.12s">
        We focus only on clinically relevant SNPs, the gene variations that actually
        matter, and skip the noise. They show where your body might need extra support,
        not what diseases you are destined to get.
      </p>
      <p class="prose" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 0.16s">
        We use them to better understand your immune function, detox capacity, and
        nutrient pathways, then fine-tune the rest of your Balance Protocol™ journey.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="genes__who panel" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 0.1s">
      <h3 class="genes__whoTitle">Who it's for</h3>
      <ul class="genes__list">
        {audience.map((a) => (
          <li>
            <svg class="genes__check" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M4 10.5l4 4 8-9" />
            </svg>
            <span>{a}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .genes__grid { display: grid; gap: var(--sp-6); }
  @media (min-width: 880px) {
    .genes__grid { grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr; gap: var(--sp-7); align-items: center; }
  }
  .genes__title { font-size: var(--step-3); margin: var(--sp-3) 0 var(--sp-4); }

  .genes__who { padding: var(--sp-5); }
  .genes__whoTitle { font-size: var(--step-1); margin-bottom: var(--sp-4); }
  .genes__list { display: grid; gap: var(--sp-3); }
  .genes__list li { display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; gap: 0.85rem; align-items: start; color: var(--muted); }
  .genes__check {
    width: 22px; height: 22px; color: var(--jade); margin-top: 2px;
    padding: 2px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: oklch(82% 0.155 158 / 0.12);
  }
</style>
